  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ、さっきの料理人みてーなの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What was up with that cook?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>びっくりした……爆発したかと思っちゃった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That scared me...I thought they 
were going to explode.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37788</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『素晴らしき青空の』……なんだっけ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>"Wonderful blue"...what was it again?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>IS THIS A REBIRTH REFERENCE</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38308</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『すばらしき味の世界』だって。
それってこの世界と違う別の世界ってことかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>"Wonderful world of flavors". They might 
be from a world outside ours.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んなもんねーよ。
ただの集まりだろ。料理同好会</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ain't no way...It's probably just a group or a 
Cooking Association or something.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう、なのかな？　後、あの変身っていうか
変装っていうか、擬態っていうか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you really think so? With that transformation...
disguise...or would camouflage fit better?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40728</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだ！　あれ、なんだよ？
いろいろおかしくないか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh I know! That was...what was it?
It's super suspicious, wasn't it?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔法……なのかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Maybe it was magic...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41728</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだとしてもさ……
アレ、誰にも見つからなかったらどーすんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even so...What would they do if no one found them?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>かなり悲惨だぞ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Isn't it kind of sad?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42420</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_191_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わからないことだらけだね……
まさに謎のシェフ……ワンダー……シェフ……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There's a lot we don't know about them...
Truly a mysterious chef...A wonder... chef...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
